    "subtitle_en": "Convert hyperscaler & AI-infra CapEx signals into implied leading-edge logic-wafer demand, 6–12 months ahead of direct customer orders. Assumptions are versioned, dated, regime-tagged data — never hardcoded constants.",
    "subtitle_zh": "把雲端巨頭與 AI 基建的 CapEx 訊號，推估為領先客戶下單 6–12 個月的隱含先進製程邏輯晶圓需求。所有假設皆為帶版本、帶日期、帶體制標籤的資料，而非寫死的常數。",
    "unit_note_en": "Wafer demand = 300mm leading-edge LOGIC wafer starts per year. HBM is memory (separate fab) and is tracked as a parallel intensity cross-check, not folded into the logic-wafer chain.",
    "unit_note_zh": "晶圓需求 = 每年 300mm 先進製程「邏輯」晶圓投片量。HBM 屬記憶體（不同晶圓廠），以平行強度指標交叉驗證，不計入邏輯晶圓鏈。",
    "domain_caveat_en": "Every numeric value below is a FLAGGED MOCK seeded by Claude for the foundry pricing team to correct. They are deliberately editable, dated and sourced — the platform's job is to make these shifting assumptions visible, not to assert them.",
    "domain_caveat_zh": "以下每個數字都是 Claude 預填、標示為待校正的假設值，供晶圓代工定價團隊修正。它們刻意可編輯、帶日期與來源——平台的目的是讓這些會漂移的假設「可見」，而非主張其為真。"
  },
